We have several packages that depend on "condor" (the Condor job
manager and Gratia's Condor probe are two notable examples), but many
sites install Condor in non-standard ways, including from
tarballs. They don't want to install our Condor RPM just to satisfy
the dependncy. Therefore this RPM claims to provide Condor, while in
fact providing nothing at all. 

And, after all, what is a lie? 'Tis but
The truth in masquerade.
